sitters.name: Marian and Roger
sitters.about: We are retired farmers, originally from Banffshire. We retired from livestock farming, after having spent more than 50 years in the industry. We are non-smokers, non-drinkers, and have our own transport.

sitters.name: Stacy
sitters.about: Currently a doctoral student in Health Sciences. Married with one adult son (professional musician), one puggle, and one cat. Hobbies: Bikram yoga, hiking/walking, outdoor activities, traveling, beaches, healthy eating, cooking.

sitters.name: Robert
sitters.about: I am a retired Police Officer, with 32 years service in the New South Wales Police Force. My best friends are my two dogs Becky and Terminator.

sitters.name: Bart and Ashton
sitters.about: We are a professional, easy-going couple in our thirties (been together for over 15 years), completely location-independent (we work online), both non-smokers, vegans/vegetarians and have no dependents. Due to the nature of our wandering lifestyle (we travel a lot), we cherish every moment at the company of animals that we get the opportunity to stay with.

sitters.name: Anthony
sitters.about: I make my own schedule. I love visiting new places, meeting new people, and animals. My purpose is to keep things running smoothly while you're away and provide necessary care.
